data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Brand New HVAC to be installed before close of escrow. This beautiful home offers granite countertops, custom cabinetry with soft pull drawers, and stainless appliance package with warranty. Home includes 4 bedrooms with 2 full baths. The primary suite features dual vanities, separate tub/shower and a huge walk-in closet. Step out back to a covered patio and a pool with dazzling waterfall. Other notable features a pre-wired surround system throughout the home. All pool equipment replaced in 2023. Paid for solar water heater, irrigation system under warranty and lastly, custom cabinetry throughout garage with adjustable shelving. A short distance from the new EOS fitness, Harkins Theater coming soon, and an array of shops and dining.
